Interface LFEdgeFactory

All Superinterfaces:
EdgeFactory<LFVertex,LFEdge>
All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultLFEdgeFactory
public interface LFEdgeFactory
extends EdgeFactory<LFVertex,LFEdge>

A factory for LF edges that creates edges from specified source and target vertices and an edge label. This interface extends the EdgeFactory interface for the specialized case of directed, labeled LF edges with LF vertices as their nodes. A default implementation is provided in DefaultLFEdgeFactory.

Author:
Scott Martin
